channel.title: Adding 317 cache to a new client
channel.description: i downloaded a 317 cache and i have a already made client. how exactly do i put this together?

item.title: Adding 317 cache to a new client
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

First find your signlink class in the “sign” folder and search for:

 public static final String findcachedir()

You should see something like: " s = “file_store_32/”;"
This is what the cache is called. Copy the name, the this case file_store_32, and name the folder containing the cache files with the same name.
Now stick that newly renamed folder into your client folder and everything should work.

If you have have any problems dont be afraid to ask.
